  "detailed_description": "<h1>⭐️CARDS AND BADGES⭐️</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/e777e709e951912a5256f68ca262f3a9.avif?t=1761592498\" width=600 height=170 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/3c1df73243e5ea9f8a699e33b741b890.avif?t=1761592498\" width=605 height=157 /></span><br>Haven't you been on vacation for a long time? Tired of the bustle of the city, endless stress, and loneliness?<br>You should take a break and experience amazing delight in the best traditions of Neko Beach.<br>At Neko Beach girls are hot by the sun and they are waiting for you with attention and shamelessness. And of course, there are the sea and palm trees.<br><br>Easy win:<br>Keyboard Сtrl+D - Complete Level<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/3a04af70b9952118cee8f67f936f6d1b.poster.avif?t=1761592498\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/3a04af70b9952118cee8f67f936f6d1b.webm?t=1761592498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/3a04af70b9952118cee8f67f936f6d1b.mp4?t=1761592498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Game Feature:</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Artworks<br></li><li>12 cute girls<br></li><li>Relaxing music<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/b93a65215bc428e8eff7f7df3e021f70.avif?t=1761592498\" width=605 height=400 /></span><br>Neko Beach is a puzzle game, in which all you need is to swop bricks, in order to make the pictures restored.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/3c1df73243e5ea9f8a699e33b741b890.avif?t=1761592498\" width=605 height=157 /></span><br>Haven't you been on vacation for a long time? Tired of the bustle of the city, endless stress, and loneliness?<br>You should take a break and experience amazing delight in the best traditions of Neko Beach.<br>At Neko Beach girls are hot by the sun and they are waiting for you with attention and shamelessness. And of course, there are the sea and palm trees.<br><br>Easy win:<br>Keyboard Сtrl+D - Complete Level<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/3a04af70b9952118cee8f67f936f6d1b.poster.avif?t=1761592498\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/3a04af70b9952118cee8f67f936f6d1b.webm?t=1761592498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/3a04af70b9952118cee8f67f936f6d1b.mp4?t=1761592498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Game Feature:</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Artworks<br></li><li>12 cute girls<br></li><li>Relaxing music<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1630650/extras/b93a65215bc428e8eff7f7df3e021f70.avif?t=1761592498\" width=605 height=400 /></span><br>Neko Beach is a puzzle game, in which all you need is to swop bricks, in order to make the pictures restored.</li></ul>",
